                <div class="row center-aligned-row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                        <img src="../uploads/images/ATP Annual Report 2017-2018 Copy.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        {% autoescape %}
                            <p><p>The approximate average income for a family in these remote villages is less than $200 per month, according to interviews conducted by ATP. Often, families live off the produce of their land, or receive a modest pension or children&#39;s allowance from the government.</p>

                            <p>The BYN program allows them to almost double their income, giving them more financial stability and, in many cases, helping them to avoid leaving the country for work.</p>
                            </p>
                        {% endautoescape %}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row backyard-nurseries-info-panel-wrapper center-aligned-row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                        {% autoescape %}
                            <p>
                            <p>ATP created the BYN Program as a way to increase their overall tree yield and offer remote villagers economic opportunity.</p>

                            <p>&nbsp;</p>

                            <p>Backyard Nursery Sponsors will receive reports from the family throughout the year with updates on the progress and results of their support.</p>
                            </p>
                        {% endautoescape %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12 backyard-nurseries-info-panel">
                        {% autoescape %}
                            <h5>Sponsorship Level</h5>
                            <p>$1,000/yr for two years</p>
                            <h5>Number Of Seedlings Per Nursery</h5>
                            <p>1,200-1,500</p>
                            <h5>Nursery Time Period</h5>
                            <p>2-3 years</p>
                            <h5>Expected Tree Yield</h5>
                            <p>85%</p>
                        {% endautoescape %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="acknowledgment-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                        <img src="../uploads/images/backyard-photo-two.jpg" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                        {% autoescape %}
